name: Ina'nis - Operation: Bonk-Bonk (Not_Shu)
description:
Hololive fangame. No game of this title has ever existed before frfr.

Controls:

Movement: Walk with left/right arrow keys, jump with up arrow key

High jump: C key

Long jump: C key + Left/right arrow key

Melee attack: Z key

Ranged attack: X key

Strong attack: Z key (during high/long jump)

Pause: D key

Enter/exit full screen: F key
